name: MusicVideo
desc: A music item that represents a music video.

items.name: static func == (MusicVideo, MusicVideo) -> Bool
items.desc: Returns a Boolean value indicating whether two values are equal.

items.name: var albumTitle: String?
items.desc: The title of the album the music video appears on.

items.name: var albums: MusicItemCollection<Album>?
items.desc: The music video’s associated albums.

items.name: var artistName: String
items.desc: The artist’s name.

items.name: var artistURL: URL?
items.desc: The artist’s URL.

items.name: var artists: MusicItemCollection<Artist>?
items.desc: The music video’s associated artists.

items.name: var artwork: Artwork?
items.desc: The artwork for the music video.

items.name: var contentRating: ContentRating?
items.desc: The rating of the content.

items.name: var duration: TimeInterval?
items.desc: The duration of the music video.

items.name: var editorialNotes: EditorialNotes?
items.desc: The editorial notes for the music video.

items.name: var genreNames: [String]
items.desc: The names of the music video’s associated genres.

items.name: var genres: MusicItemCollection<Genre>?
items.desc: The music video’s associated genres.

items.name: var has4K: Bool?
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the music video has 4K content.

items.name: var hasHDR: Bool?
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether the music video has HDR10-encoded content.

items.name: var hashValue: Int
items.desc: The hash value.

items.name: let id: MusicItemID
items.desc: The unique identifier for the music video.

items.name: var isPreview: Bool
items.desc: A Boolean value that indicates whether this content corresponds to a subscription video preview.

items.name: var isrc: String?
items.desc: The International Standard Recording Code (ISRC) for the music video.

items.name: var moreByArtist: MusicItemCollection<MusicVideo>?
items.desc: A collection of additional music videos by the artist.

items.name: var moreInGenre: MusicItemCollection<MusicVideo>?
items.desc: A collection of music videos in the same genre as this music video.

items.name: var playParameters: PlayParameters?
items.desc: The parameters to use to play the music video.

items.name: var previewAssets: [PreviewAsset]?
items.desc: The preview assets for the music video.

items.name: var releaseDate: Date?
items.desc: The release date (or expected prerelease date) for the music video.

items.name: var songs: MusicItemCollection<Song>?
items.desc: The music video’s associated songs.

items.name: var title: String
items.desc: The title of the music video.

items.name: var trackNumber: Int?
items.desc: The music video’s number in the album’s track list.

items.name: var url: URL?
items.desc: The URL for the music video.

items.name: var workName: String?
items.desc: For classical music only, the name of the associated work.

items.name: func hash(into: inout Hasher)
items.desc: Hashes the essential components of this value by feeding them into the given hasher.

items.name: typealias ID
items.desc: A type representing the stable identity of the entity associated with an instance.
